1. *On* je bio izuzetno sposoban za tu vrstu posla. (He was exceptionally capable for that kind of job.) 
2. *Sposobna* je bila da prepozna pogrešne odluke. (She was capable of recognizing wrong decisions.)
3. *Sposobnost* da se prilagodi promenama je bila njegova najveća prednost. (The ability to adapt to changes was his biggest advantage.)
4. Radila je sa ljudima koji su bili jako *sposobni*. (She was working with people who were very capable.)
5. Ona je bila u stanju da iskoristi svoju *sposobnost*. (She was able to use her capability.)